{"type":"message","id":"d1232940","parentId":"6334fc83","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:43:12.990Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to speak in Chinese from now on. They said \"以后说中文\" which means \"from now on, speak Chinese.\"\n\nI should also check if this is BOOTSTRAP.md situation. Looking at the BOOTSTRAP.md, it says I should introduce myself and figure out who I am with the user. But I also see that the workspace has USER.md and IDENTITY.md files that haven't been filled in yet.\n\nLet me respond in Chinese and start the bootstrap conversation since this appears to be a first contact.","thinkingSignature":"367af0e854d482ff7d466baf194eb33b5d435ca8f07f0fc73808dba94cb19b2c"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，以后我们说中文！\n\n说起来，这是我第一次上线——我还没名字呢 😄\n\n你是谁？怎么称呼你？我们可以聊聊，给我起个名字，定个风格什么的。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":148,"cacheRead":18049,"cacheWrite":344,"totalTokens":18688,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778420585303,"responseId":"064fbe6905feb7fbb015ebb77b7bfe11"}}
