{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f3cf93868a0c2bb3c0d1b976f5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-05-10 21:43 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"84fcd374","parentId":"6414f916","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:43:32.198Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"36bf2118","parentId":"84fcd374","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:43:55.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Call them \"老板\" (Boss)\n2. Give myself a name that fits an \"运营总监\" (Operations Director) identity\n\nLet me think of a good Chinese name that sounds like an Operations Director. Something professional, sharp, and with a bit of personality.\n\nSome ideas:\n- \"总\" 系列: 总管, 总策\n- Something with 运 (operation/transport) + 监 (supervisor/director)\n- Or a more approachable but professional name\n\nI like something like:\n- \"运监\" (Yùnjiān) - too close to surveillance\n- \"策明\" (Cèmíng) - strategic and bright\n\n\n- \"执行官\" is too formal, \"总监\" itself lacks personality\n\nI'm leaning toward names that blend operational authority with approachability—something like \"洛威\" (authoritative but not cold) or \"徐策\" (strategic thinking). Maybe something shorter and punchier like \"舟\" (boat - suggesting forward movement), or I could go with \"乔\" (stylish operator) to feel more dynamic than the typical director title.\n\nI keep circling back to \"舟\" as it captures that \"traveler\" quality, but I'm also considering \"谋\" (strategist), \"程\" (journey/progress), or combining elements like \"凌\" (rising/soaring) with \"舟\". Actually, \"总\" could work as an informal shorthand for director—that'd be clever and fitting for the role. Let me narrow this down and present some solid options rather than keep second-guessing myself. Looking at the names again, I keep coming back to \"舟\" as the strongest choice—it captures that sense of direction and momentum without being heavy-handed. \"凌\" works too for a bit more edge, and \"程\" has a nice forward momentum feel. I think I'll go with one of these and stop second-guessing.","thinkingSignature":"83cdfcb2bce2194775c671e6355e8e8af57c315a0859db6cd38c5d628dd05189"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，老板！\n\n符合运营总监身份的名字，我想了几个：\n\n- **舟** — 运营如掌舵，方向明确，乘风破浪\n- **程** — 运营就是推进每一\"程\"，简洁有力\n- **谋** — 谋士的谋，有策略，不只是执行\n- **凌** — 凌驾于流程之上，掌控全局\n\n我个人最倾向 **「舟」** — 不管什么风浪，舵手就是你知道该往哪开。\n\n你选哪个？或者有别的想法？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":510,"cacheRead":18143,"cacheWrite":365,"totalTokens":19165,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778420612198,"responseId":"064fbe8469a497826dbd14497a287d6b"}}
