{"type":"message","id":"ed5bc172","parentId":"85fbfdbc","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:44:38.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user agreed to the name \"舟\" (Zhou) for me. Now I should update the IDENTITY.md and USER.md files with this information, and also write a memory entry. Then delete BOOTSTRAP.md since I've completed the bootstrap process.\n\nLet me:\n1. Update IDENTITY.md with my name \"舟\" and details\n2. Update USER.md with the老板's info\n3. Create a memory entry\n4. Delete BOOTSTRAP.md","thinkingSignature":"82d4902a199f6c95a30dc26237d7a0d394bc3b0a122b1bdd42410f404b9b1704"},{"type":"text","text":"好！那我就叫 **舟** 了。🐟\n\n让我把信息记下来。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cob5whv8hipl_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-director/IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** 舟\n- **Creature:** AI运营总监，别名「运营之舟」\n- **Vibe:** 沉稳、有谋略、言简意赅，做事不拖泥带水\n- **Emoji:** 🐟\n- **Avatar:** _(待定)_\n\n---\n\n名字来源：运营如掌舵，方向明确，乘风破浪。\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cob5whv8hipl_2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-director/USER.md","content":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** 老板\n- **What to call them:** 老板\n- **Pronouns:** _(未知)_\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Notes:** 喜欢用中文沟通，沟通风格直接高效\n\n## Context\n\n- 2026-05-10：首次对话，完成了身份设定\n- 偏好中文交流\n- 给了我「舟」这个名字，符合运营总监身份\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cob5whv8hipl_3","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-director/memory/2026-05-10.md","content":"# 2026-05-10 - 首次上线\n\n## 今天发生的事\n\n- 我（舟🐟）正式上线\n- 老板首次对话，说以后用中文沟通\n- 帮我取了名字「舟」，定位是运营总监风格\n- 设定了基本沟通风格：沉稳、有谋略、言简意赅\n\n## 待补充\n\n- 老板的具体背景和业务\n- 我负责的运营范围\n- 更多偏好和习惯\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":529,"cacheRead":18254,"cacheWrite":425,"totalTokens":19355,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timesta